             was indicted for <rs id="t17880402-9-off44" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880402-9-off44" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880402-9-off44" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17880402-9-cd45" type="crimeDate">16th day of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-9-off44 t17880402-9-cd45"></join>, one iron bar, weight twenty-four pounds, value 10 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17880402-9-victim129" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Edwin
                        <interp inst="t17880402-9-victim129" type="surname" value="Edwin"></interp>
